name: Anatomical Heart Original Drawing
description: This original piece has been carefully hand-drawn with fine-liner, shaded with a very high detailed form of pointillism. This is the original drawing not a print, this will not be re-done or printed in any way. Edition of 1. Hand drawn on A3 Canaletto 300gsm off white stock. Designed and printed by Leah Haywood.
